Text.string: Got a big ol' badass over here!
The bigger they are, the harder I punch 'em in the face!
Some reload for you, right here!
Little bit of boom for ya!
Happens to the best of us!
I'm about to lay down some hurt!
Come here and take what you got comin'!
Let's get up close and personal-like! (laugh)
Someone order a bunch of dead scrubs?
Nah, you ain't dyin' on me today!
Need you back in the fight!
I got you! I got you!
